Ana gudanar da bincike kan cutar korona (COVID-19) a Majalisar Tarayyar Turai/Taron Tarayyar Turai da Majalisar Burtaniya, 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Masu kamuwa da cutar korona da ke tattare da cutar (COVID-19) suna nuna rashin daidaito a cikin tarayyar Turai/Turai na Turai da kuma Majalisar Ingila da ke kula da cutar, kuma a wasu lokuta, COVID-19 yana gudana cikin sauri a duk faɗin duniya.
Idan muka lura da abin da ya faru a Italiya, dole ne jihohi, asibitoci da kungiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya su kara tsarawa saboda yawan mutanen da ke fama da cutar COVID-19 da ke da ciwon sukari a jiki, da kuma yawan cututtukan da ke faruwa a jiki.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, wani rukuni na kwayoyin cuta da ba a san su ba ya bayyana a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Hukumar Kula da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta bayyana cewa cutar coronavirus ta biyu da aka gano a matsayin cutar huhu ta coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ba za ta iya haifar da cutar ba.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, ana kiran cutar ta SARS-CoV cutar (COVI-19).
Wani bincike ya nuna cewa kusan kashi 80 cikin dari na mutane suna da cututtuka masu tsanani, kamar rashin lafiyar numfashi, da kuma rashin lafiya.
A cikin kashi 14% na masu kamuwa da cutar, COVID-19 yana haifar da kamuwa da cutar da kuma hana su rayuwa a asibiti kuma kashi 6% na marasa lafiya suna fama da cutar kuma dole ne likitocin su kula da su.
Mutuwar marasa lafiya a asibiti na COVID-19 zai kai kashi 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, muna nazarin yanayin cutar COVID-19 da ke faruwa a kowace ƙasa na Majalisar Turai/EEA da kuma Majalisar Dinkin Duniya (UK) da ke cikin lardin Hubei, China.
Ina kuma duba yawan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Birtaniya da kuma wadanda ke Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Birtaniya
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya mamaye wasu wurare kuma a yanzu ana samun ci gaba da cutar COVID-19 a sauran sassan duniya.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta bayyana cewa COVID-19 cuta ce ta duniya.
A cikin rahoton Eurosurveillance na 5 ga Maris, 2020, Spiteri al. ya ba da rahoton cewa an sami adadin mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 a Turai bisa ga WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, an fara samun kamuwa da cutar ta uku a Faransa a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 a cikin masu dawowa daga birnin Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an samu kamuwa da COVID-19 a kasashe 30 na EU/EEA da kuma a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda a tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da wannan lokacin an samu kamuwa da cutar 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 da kuma mutuwar 1,441 a wasu ƙasashe na Italiya.
Kula da yawan adadin masu cutar COVID-19
A cewar Hukumar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), adadin adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka ba da rahoton daga masu amincewa kamar Shugabannin Hukumar Lafiya, Shugabannin Kasashen Cikin Gida da na Birane da kuma WHO ba za a bincika duk wani abu da ya faru ba da safe da karfe 8:00 na safe.
Wannan bayanin da aka yi amfani da shi don gwajin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da kuma a Birtaniya, yana gwadawa da na Italiya.
Bisa ga binciken da aka yi na yawan masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19, mun ƙidaya yawan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19, wanda ya ƙidaya yawan kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da kuma ƙasar Burtaniya daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma gano cewa, adadin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar da aka samu a kowace ƙasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8:00 na yamma ya shafi ƙasar Italiya daga ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Matsayi na COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Birtaniya.
Ƙaddamar da ƙididdigar yawan adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA a cikin kwanaki 14 da Birtaniya ya biyo bayan babban adadin na Hubei Province (China) (Hotuna 1).
A cikin EU/EEA da Birtaniya duka, adadin adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 ya fara karuwa ne a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu kuma ya ci gaba ne a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (Abubuwa da yawa).
Mafi yawan abin da ya sa wannan ya faru shi ne yawan adadin wadanda aka samu a Italiya, amma sauran kasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya sun samu irin wannan ci gaban a cikin adadin COVID-19 (Abin da ya sa).
Hoton na 2 ya nuna yadda ake samun adadin kamuwa da cutar COVID-19, a cikin EU/EEA da Birtaniya a lokacin da aka samu a Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya bayyana cewa, a ranar 15 ga watan Maris da karfe 8:00 na yammacin yammacin rana, kasashe 15 na EU/EEA da wasu kasashe na Birtaniya sun ba da rahoton adadin wadanda za su kamu da cutar a Italiya a cikin kwanaki 3 kafin ko bayan kammala.
Rahotanni sun nuna cewa adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 da aka ruwaito ba su da iyaka ga EU/EEA da Birtaniya.
Matsayin da muke fuskanta na COVID-19 ya nuna cewa cutar tana da tasiri sosai wanda zai iya zama sanarwa a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan shi ne saboda ƙasashe suna cikin wani yanayi na rashin daidaito, canje-canje a cikin takardun da ke tattare da lafiyar ƙasa, da kuma bayyanar cututtuka daban-daban a cikin ƙasashe da kuma wasu hanyoyin da za a iya gano marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar sake duba lafiyarsu don COVID-19, da kuma sake dubawa.
A farkon watan Maris na shekarar 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya sun gano cewa kashi 10% na mutanen da ke fama da COVID-19 suna bukatar kula da lafiya kuma rahotanni sun ce asibitoci da kungiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya a yankunan sun ci gaba da kula da lafiyarsu.
Bayanai na asibitoci da/ko kungiyoyin masu kula da cutar COVID-19 suna cikin EU/EEA na kashi 6% da 1% na masu cutar, dabam dabam (da kuma bayanan da aka ba su).
Sai kuma a haɗa su duka a cikin wani wuri don a yi amfani da bayanan kula da yawan waɗanda suka kamu da cutar da kuma yawan waɗanda suka mutu.
Wani bincike a shekara ta 2010-2011 ya nuna cewa akwai canji a cikin yawan gado da kuma yawan wuraren da ake kula da marasa lafiya a Turai, daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 a Portugal ga mutane 100,000.
