Wani binciken da aka yi na PCR da CT a Wuhan a lokacin da cutar ta fara ya nuna cewa CT ta fi dacewa da PCR, ko da yake ba a amince da shi ba, kuma ana iya samun hotunan hoto na zamani da sauran cututtukan pneumonia da cututtukan cutar.
A watan Maris na shekarar 2020, Kwalejin Radiology ta Amirka ta ce "ba za a iya amfani da CT ba don ganewa ko a matsayin hanyar farko na magance COVID-19". A watan Maris na shekarar 2020, CDC ta soke PCR don ganewa na farko.
A matsayin tushen tsarin rigakafi na mutum, ana samar da kwayoyin halitta kamar IgM da IgG.
Zai iya zama da amfani wajen gano cutar a cikin mutane tun daga farkon kwanaki 7 ko makamancin haka bayan bayyanar cututtuka, don gano nauyi, da kuma a cikin kulawar jama'a. Ana iya samun cututtuka ta hanyar cibiyar gwaji (CLT) ko kuma ta hanyar gwajin asibiti (PoCT).
Tsarin gwaji na zamani a cikin dakunan gwaje-gwaje da yawa na iya ƙayyade waɗannan shigarwar amma kasancewa su a cikin sauƙi ya dogara da yawan fitarwa na kowane tsari.
Ana amfani da CLT a cikin jini wanda yawanci ana amfani da shi a cikin jiki, ko da yake ana iya amfani da kwayoyin da ke bin shi don bin tsarin rigakafin jiki.
Ana daukar cutar PoCT ta hanyar zubar da jini ta hanyar yin allurar rigakafi.
Ba kamar tsarin PCR ba, matakin da aka bayar zai zama mai amfani kafin a yi gwaji. A ranar 26 ga Maris, 2020, FDA ta lissafa abubuwa 29 da ke ba da bayanan asibiti kamar yadda aka sani kuma yanzu za su iya yin gwajin likita.
A ranar 7 ga Afrilu, 2020, an gudanar da gwajin gwaji guda daya wanda FDA ta amince da shi don magance aikin gaggawa. A karshen watan Maris na 2020, Euroimmun Medical Laboratory Diagnostics da Epitope Diagnostics sun samu nasarar tabbatar da cutar.
Yawan gwajin zai iya yin gwajin jini a cikin kwayoyin halitta kuma ya fi sauri fiye da gwajin RNA na kwayar PCR da aka sani.
Ana lura da masu ilimin likitanci a cikin kwanaki 14 bayan fara cutar. A farkon watan Afrilu, Ingila za ta sami wani daga cikin kayan aikin gwajin likitancin da ya sayi da kuma amfani da su.
