Wani bincike na nazarin 70 ya nuna cewa yin amfani da kayan wanke hannu a cikin jama'a yana da muhimmanci wajen rage yawan wanke hannu a LMIC, wani lokaci kuma yana da tasiri ga jama'a don sayen kayan wanke hannu ga yara. Wani dalili kuma na cewa rashin amfani da wanke hannu a makarantu shine abin da ake kira "Mataki na Uku" ta UNICEF wanda ke ƙarfafa makarantu su ɗauki matakan da suka dace don tabbatar da cewa ɗalibai suna wanke hannayensu da sabulu, a tsakanin sauran hanyoyin tsabtace hannu.
Idan an samu tarurruka na farko, za a iya samun ci gaba daga kashi ɗaya zuwa uku.
