Hanyoyin haɗari a wurin aiki don COVID-19
Kula da haɗarin aiki na COVID-19 shine tsarin da za a yi amfani da shi a cikin yanayin aiki da kuma kiwon lafiya don hana cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Manufofin tsaro a wurin aiki sun bambanta da wurin aiki da kuma irin aikin da ake yi, dangane da kimanta haɗarin zama, yadda ake kamuwa da cutar a cikin al'umma, da kuma abubuwan da ke sa ma'aikata su kamu da COVID-19.
Hukumar Kula da Lafiya da Lafiya a Aiki ta Amurka (OSHA) ta ce, irin wannan aikin ba shi da haɗari ga yin amfani da manyan motoci tare da jama'a ko ma'aikata, wanda ake ba da shawarar matakan rigakafin farko, kamar wanke hannu, hana wasu ma'aikata zama a gida idan sun kamu da cutar, kula da numfashi, da kuma tsabtace da kuma tsabtace wuraren aiki.
