A ranar 28 ga Maris, 2020, FDA ta ba da umarnin gaggawa na amfani da hydroxychloroquine da chloroquine ba tare da sanarwa ga likitoci da ke kula da maganin COVID-19 ba. Rahoton bincike na 7 ya haɗa da interferon, ribavirin ko umifenovir don magance COVID-19.
Bayanai na farko sun nuna cewa ribavirin yana da amfani ga maganin SARS-CoV-2 a cikin vitro.
An ba da shawarar yin nazarin nitzoxanide a cikin vivo bayan an gano cewa ƙwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 tana raguwa. Nazarin ya nuna cewa gano farkon furotin mai ƙyama ta hanyar transmembrane protease serine 2 (TMPRSS2) yana da mahimmanci ga SARS-CoV-2 ta hanyar aiki tare da mai karɓar ACE2.
Bincike game da chloroquine da hydroxychloroquine da ko ba tare da azithromycin ba ya hana masu amfani da magunguna su karɓa ba tare da ƙarin bincike ba. Oseltamivir yana hana SARS-CoV-2 a cikin vitro kuma yana da muhimmiyar rawa wajen magance COVID-19.
Cytokine zai iya zama haɗari a wasu cututtukan COVID-19 masu cutarwa.
Akwai kuma tabbacin cewa hydroxychloroquine na iya samun damar gano tsarin cytokine. Tocilizumab an shigar da shi cikin tsarin magani ta Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta kasar Sin bayan kammala wani karamin bincike.
An gudanar da wani bincike na biyu na rashin zabe a kasar Italiya domin gano cutar a cikin mutane da kuma kamuwa da cutar.
Tare da gwajin jini na jini don gano wani cytokine, aikin shi ne hana irin wannan ci gaba, wanda zai iya zama sanadin mutuwa ga wasu mutane da ke fama da cutar.
Maganin interleukin-6 antagonist mai karɓa ya yi watsi da FDA bisa ga binciken da aka yi na maganin cytokine mai karɓa na steroid wanda ya samo asali daga maganin CAR T cell, a shekara ta 2017.
Amma, ko kuma wani irin wannan bincike, da aka yi a kan batun ya nuna cewa tocilizumab yana da muhimmanci wajen magance CRS.
Bayyana magungunan da ke da tsabta da kuma haɗuwa da magungunan da ke cikin mutanen da ake bi da su don COVID-19 ga mutanen da ke da bukata ya dogara da gwaji a matsayin hanyar kariya ta rashin sani.
Wannan tsarin zai kasance ne don SARS amma zai samar da yara.
Ana amfani da kwayar cutar a matsayin hanyar aiki ta hanyar maganin kwayoyin cuta wanda zai iya nuna kariya ga SARS-CoV-2.
Wasu dalilai, kamar ƙwayoyin cytotoxity da/ko cin abinci, na iya zama.
Irin wannan magani ta hanyar likitan da ya san shi, alal misali, ta hanyar likitan da ke da kafa ɗaya, yana tafiya.
Bayyana jini ga wani mai jinya, wanda shine ruwan jini da aka kawo ga marasa lafiya da suka ci kuma suna da ƙwayoyin cuta, zai iya zama da wuya ga amsawa da kuma rashin lafiya.
Cutar korona, wata ƙungiya ta cututtuka
Li Wenliang, likita a asibitin Wuhan na tsakiya, wanda ya kamu da COVID-19 kuma ya mutu bayan ya yi kira ga jama'a su yi hankali da yaduwar cutar.
